Challenge: Inconsistent Access Control
Impact: Risk of breaches, non-compliance
Recommended Strategy: Role-based access and approval workflows
Principle: Compliance

Lack of Accountability
Issues remain unresolved
Develop Standard Operating Procedures and create a RACI matrix
